<h3>Speed of Expiration of <span t:replace="feed getTitle" /></h3>
<p>On channels with more fleeting content (for example, music videos or video blogs), you might want videos that you've watched to expire more quickly to make way for new content. Remember, you can permanently keep any video that hasn't expired yet by clicking 'save'.</p>

